product_name: POTATOES RUSSET | Fresh Produce | Bulk 20 LBS | Grown in USA
description: Along with rice and wheat, potatoes are one of most important staple crop. Russet potatoes are also a good source of minerals. You can use russet potatoes to make baked potatoes, mashed potatoes, French fries or pureed soups.
